title: Warm Steak, Kale & Sweet Potato Salad Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: You’ll serve thinly sliced garlic-and-thyme steak over a beautifully balanced kale salad packed with tender browned sweet potato and topped with Parmesan cheese. It’s dressed in a creamy balsamic dressing and topped off with crunchy pecans and chewy dried cranberries for a light-but-hearty lunch you’ll have on the table in a quick 15!
